  "text": "The transformation process is thus in the form graphite-liquid carbon-diamond (compare to the work of X.D. Ren et al. [CITATION_1] ). The presence of a liquid phase is essential, since the model considers the nucleation and the growth of diamond crystals in an undercooled liquid.",
